<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    COMING UP: MUCH MORE OF THE SAME
 &HT;    Moving in (k) commentary and (f) financial categories for
release Sunday, Dec. 19.
 &HT;    By MARILYN GEEWAX
 &HT;    c.1999 Cox News Service
