rebuilt. When residents are hurt in car crashes, family and friends
volunteer to make homes wheelchair-accessible. What happened here
in Jaffrey in 1999 is about greater gifts, lasting gifts, that
soothe and bind. By Irene Sege. (2 takes)
</P>
