<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1999-12-16 13:46 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A0869 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u a BC-COMPUTERS-PALM-BOS &LR;      12-16 1002
