striking down the use of race in police department promotions would
have been quickly appealed by a department intent on a diverse
command staff. But the legal landscape has changed dramatically as
the US Supreme Court issued rulings restricting race as criteria in
employment, government contracting and school admissions. By Sacha
Pfeiffer. 800 words.
