   GEORGIA-E-COMMERCE. In this new age of electronic commerce, how
is the temporary moratorium on taxing Internet sales affecting the
Augusta area? Are local retailers having a hard time competing with
the cheaper online sales? What would a reduction in sales tax
revenues mean for local and state governments? (Working.) By
Elizabeth Hurt
