growth in employment and foreign sales in 1997. (250 words.) By
Laura Winter
</P>
<P>
   WYOMING-WRI. Federal researchers today praised an amendment
introduced this year by Rep. Barbara Cubin, R-Wyo., to help highway
builders around the country learn how to construct better roads.
(600 words.) Barney McManigal
</P>
<P>
   -30-
