 (Eds.: Newspapers that used the Boston Globe story
ISRAEL-MILLENNIUM (i) by Charles M. Sennott, which moved Tuesday,
Dec. 14, will wish to use the following corrective.
<TEXT>
<P>
   &LR;  &QL;
</P>
<P>
   A Boston Globe article about millennium activities in Israel
misstated the time when the Muslim holy month of Ramadan will end.
Ramadan will end with the arrival of the new moon, which is
expected on or just after Jan. 6.
