</P>
<P>
   INTEL-PLANT (Udnated) _ Intel will pour $800 million into the
Hudson, Mass. chip plant it bought from Digital Equipment Corp., an
investment that will create 450 new high-tech manufacturing jobs.
By Hiawatha Bray. 700 words.
</P>
