slowly, that is all changing, as more minorities find themselves in
powerful positions in the advocacy and policy front, and state and
federal dollars are starting to be newly appropriated in
recognition of where the disease now hits home. By Jennifer
Steinhauer. (The story has moved in ``a'' news file.) 1,600 words.
