   (NYT40) NEW YORK -- Dec. 16, 1999 -- NY-MILLENNIUM-NETWORKS --
Peter Jennings at the ABC News millennium planning meeting Monday
in New York. Jennings will anchor ABC's all-millennium,
all-the-time broadcast, from 5 a.m. on the last day of the old year
until 5 a.m. on the first day of the new. (Richard Perry/The New
York Times)
