<HEADLINE>
QUOTATION OF THE DAY
</HEADLINE>
 (Eds.: This quotation refers to BC-RUSSIA-CHECHNYA-NYT, which moved
in ``i'' news file.)  
 c.1999 N.Y. Times News Service   
<TEXT>
<P>
   ``I had to leave today because I could be dead tomorrow if I
stayed.''
</P>
<P>
   _ABDRAZAK DOVLETMIRZAYEV, 64, a Grozny refugee.
</P>
</TEXT>
