<HEADLINE>
TRIBAL BUDGET SOARS TO $68 MILLION 
</HEADLINE>
   (For use by N.Y. Times News Service clients)  
 By CAROL SOWERS  
 c.1999 The Arizona Republic  
<TEXT>
<P>
   Faced with an uproar among tribal members who say they aren't
getting their fair share, the Salt River Pima-Maricopa Indian Com
munity unveiled its annual budget, $68 million, a $25 million
